<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.2">
<l>vallinu ṇitaḻaṉ ṉavāṭai koṇṭu</l>
<l rend="indent">vacaiyaṟat tiruvarai virittu ṭuttu</l>
<l>pallinuṇpaṟ ṟākavu ṭaivāḷ cāttip</l>
<l rend="indent">paṇaikkaccun tippala taḻai naṭuvē</l>
<l>mullainal naṟumalar vēṅkai malar</l>
<l rend="indent">aṇintupal lāyarku ḻāmna ṭuvē</l>
<l>elliyam pōtākap piḷḷai varum</l>
<l rend="indent">etirniṉṟaṅ kiṉavaḷai yiḻavēṉmi ṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Don’t stand there obstructing the boy</l>
<l rend="indent">when he comes during the evening</l>
<l>in the midst of a group of many herders adorned by jasmine blossoms</l>
<l rend="indent">with good fragrance and Kino tree blossoms</l>
<l>in the middle of many peacock feathers on [his] big waist sash,</l>
<l rend="indent">wearing a dagger as thin as a lizard,</l>
<l>with garments like the slender leaves of a creeper</l>
<l rend="indent">spreading over, adorning his faultless holy hips,</l>
<l>[and] lose your bunch of bangles.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
